## 2026-04-03 - Generator panel dry-run preview mode
- Added `dryRun()` method to `GeneratorService` that computes a full diff (created/updated/unchanged/deleted) without persisting — compares `computeResults()` output against the token store, and detects deleted tokens by scanning for generator-tagged tokens in the target group not present in the preview output
- Added `POST /api/generators/:id/dry-run` route in generators.ts (registered before `:id/check-overwrites` and `:id/run` to ensure static sub-segment wins)
- Added `DryRunDiff` interface, `DryRunPreview` component, and `handlePreviewOutput` to `GeneratorPipelineCard` in GraphPanel.tsx; the card now has a "Preview output" button in the actions bar that fetches the diff inline, shows summary pills (+N new, ~M changed, -K removed, =P unchanged) that are clickable to expand detail lists with old→new values, and a "Run (apply N changes)" confirm button

