## 2026-04-03 - ComparePanel has no "show differences only" toggle
- Added `showDiffsOnly` state (default `false`) with a "Diffs only" toggle button in the header toolbar, disabled when all values are identical.
- Computed `aliasDiffers` and `scopesDiffer` alongside existing `rowDiffs` to correctly gate all four row types (type, alias, property keys, scopes) when the toggle is active.
- The toggle button shows a yellow-tinted active state to indicate the filter is on; `anyDiff` gates the disabled state so the button is greyed out when tokens are identical.

